            'body_value' => '!!Software I Like\r\nI recommend using everything on this page if it is applicable to you.\r\n\r\n!!!Operating System\r\n* Windows Preferred: Windows 7\r\n* Linux/*NIX Preferred: Debian\r\n* Apple Preferred: None/Debian/Windows 7\r\n\r\n!!!Software (Windows)\r\n!!!! Security\r\n* Anti-Spyware: [[http://www.safer-networking.org/en/download/|SpyBot Search and Destroy]]\r\n* Anti-Virus:  [[http://free.avg.com/us-en/download-avg-anti-virus-free|AVG Free]]\r\n\r\n!!!! Utilities\r\n* Instant Messaging: [[http://www.pidgin.im/download/|Pidgin]]\r\n* Image Viewing/Resizing/Converting: [[http://www.irfanview.com/main_download_engl.htm|Irfanview]]\r\n* Web Browser: [[http://www.google.com/chrome|Chrome]]\r\n* Web Browser: [[http://www.mozilla.com/en-US/products/download.html|FireFox]]\r\n* File Zip/Unzip/Compression: [[http://www.7-zip.org/|7-zip]]\r\n* Editor: [[http://notepad-plus-plus.org/download|Notepad++]]\r\n\r\n\r\n!!!! Media Players\r\n* [[http://www.videolan.org/vlc/|VLC]]\r\n* [[http://www.free-codecs.com/download/QuickTime_Alternative.htm|QuickTime Alternative]]\r\n* [[http://www.free-codecs.com/download/real_alternative.htm|RealPlayer Alternative ]]\r\n* [[http://www.free-codecs.com/download/media_player_classic.htm|Media Player Classic]]\r\n* [[http://get.adobe.com/flashplayer/|Flash Player]]\r\n',
