            'body_value' => '** I haven\'t completed this game **\r\n\r\nMaybe someday this will be a full page, for now it\'s just a place for me to keep my notes I want to throw away.\r\n\r\n** Magic **\r\nAncestor\'s Wrath\r\nCandlelight\r\nClairvoyance\r\nFast Healing\r\nFire Rune\r\nFirebolt\r\nFlames\r\nFrost Rune\r\nFrostbite\r\nFury Healing\r\nIce Rune\r\nIce Spike\r\nLesser Ward\r\nLightning Bolt\r\nLightning Rune\r\nMagelight\r\nOakflesh\r\nRaise Zombie\r\nReanimate Corpse\r\nSparks\r\nStoneflesh\r\nUnrelenting Force\r\nWhirlwind Spirit\r\nConjure Familiar\r\nConjure Flame Ant\r\nFear\r\nHealing HAnds\r\nBound Battleaxe\r\nBound Sword\r\n\r\n** Go Back To These Areas to Clear **\r\nUngol Barrow\r\nHobbs Fall Cave\r\nDragon @ Barrows?\r\nStoney Creek\r\nMizft (Master Lock)\r\nDustman\'s Cairn\r\n\r\n** NPC Locations **\r\nBlacksmith/Smelter: Windhelm\r\nEnchanter & Alchemy: Hall of Countanance\r\nGeneral Goods: Whitrun, Windhelm\r\nAlteration: Winter College - Todfer\r\nAlchemy: Whiterun - Arcadia\r\nDestruction: College - Bernalda\r\nRestoration: College - Collette\r\nConjurer: College - Finnas\r\nIllusion: College - Drevis\r\nEnchanting: College - Sengius\r\nLight Armor: Riften - Grelka\r\nBlock: Whitrun (Companion) - Njadya Stone Arm\r\n1 Handed: Whitrun (Outside) - Amren\r\nHeavy Armor: Whitrerun (Companion) - Farkas\r\nSpeech: Bards College?/Rieverwood/Wandrer? - Talsgar',
